1:37:28.740 --> 1:37:31.070
What do you think
I'll find inside?

1:37:31.270 --> 1:37:33.110
The bust of Nefertiti.

1:37:33.310 --> 1:37:35.770
The Ark of the Covenant.

1:37:35.970 --> 1:37:37.160
Maltese Falcon.

1:37:37.360 --> 1:37:38.550
Oh...

1:37:38.750 --> 1:37:39.980
Nothing more significant?

1:37:41.330 --> 1:37:42.820
What more could you want?

1:37:43.020 --> 1:37:44.720
<i>[Lecuona Cuban Boys</i>
<i>singing "Cubanacan"]</i>

1:37:46.290 --> 1:37:48.950
[indistinct chatter]

1:37:49.150 --> 1:37:51.000
<i>Cedric: So you got caught</i>
<i>in the crossfire</i>

1:37:51.200 --> 1:37:52.830
<i>between a mother</i>
<i>and a daughter?</i>

1:37:53.030 --> 1:37:54.920
Marlowe: Yep,
I never seem to learn.

1:37:55.120 --> 1:37:56.880
Cedric: And who wins,
Mr. Marlowe?

1:37:57.070 --> 1:37:58.660
The mother or the daughter?

1:37:58.860 --> 1:38:00.660
Marlowe: Who would you
put your money on?

1:38:00.860 --> 1:38:02.400
Cedric:
Well, the ambassador loses.

1:38:02.600 --> 1:38:06.280
Marlowe: Those guys never lose,
Cedric, they just move on.

1:38:06.480 --> 1:38:08.500
[Cedric chuckles]

1:38:08.690 --> 1:38:09.570
[door opens]

1:38:11.010 --> 1:38:12.540
Mr. Marlowe?

1:38:12.740 --> 1:38:13.850
Yeah.

1:38:14.050 --> 1:38:16.110
She will see you now.

1:38:16.310 --> 1:38:17.460
Thank you.

1:38:17.660 --> 1:38:18.980
[music continues]

1:38:20.590 --> 1:38:22.420
[indistinct chatter]

1:38:22.620 --> 1:38:24.850
- Mr. Marlowe.
- Mrs. Cavendish.

1:38:26.240 --> 1:38:27.860
[indistinct chatter]

1:38:28.060 --> 1:38:31.160
So, this was the transaction?

1:38:34.380 --> 1:38:37.700
- What exactly do you mean?
Thank you.

1:38:37.900 --> 1:38:41.270
You saved the ambassador's ass,
he lets you run things.

1:38:41.470 --> 1:38:44.660
It's better than the bootlegging
trade, don't you think?

1:38:44.860 --> 1:38:47.710
The ambassadors
moved beyond all that.

1:38:47.910 --> 1:38:49.880
Your mother's acting
again I see.

1:38:50.080 --> 1:38:51.830
Clare: Uh, she never stopped.

1:38:53.400 --> 1:38:54.800
What's the story?

1:38:55.000 --> 1:38:57.540
Oh, you know, like any.

1:38:57.740 --> 1:39:00.550
Love, murder, reconciliation.

1:39:00.750 --> 1:39:02.200
Marlowe: Happy ending?

1:39:02.400 --> 1:39:03.640
Mm...

1:39:03.840 --> 1:39:06.600
We're working on that.

1:39:06.800 --> 1:39:11.510
