me why I'm here, Mrs. Cavendish?

1:39:11.710 --> 1:39:14.820
The studio needs someone to
play knight in shining armor.

1:39:15.020 --> 1:39:16.350
[chuckles]

1:39:16.550 --> 1:39:18.830
I saw ten of those guys outside.

1:39:19.030 --> 1:39:20.780
They can only act the part.

1:39:20.980 --> 1:39:22.520
So I should say
my goodbyes then.

1:39:23.870 --> 1:39:26.220
The studios all
cleaned up, Mr. Marlowe.

1:39:28.960 --> 1:39:31.480
Roosevelt's an inch
from joining the war effort.

1:39:33.790 --> 1:39:36.890
The ambassador would like to...

1:39:37.090 --> 1:39:40.150
reward you for your discretion.

1:39:40.350 --> 1:39:43.240
The studio will always need
its private detective.

1:39:43.440 --> 1:39:44.970
You're offering me a job?

1:39:49.590 --> 1:39:51.770
More than a job.

1:39:51.970 --> 1:39:53.110
A pension.

1:39:54.510 --> 1:39:56.900
Executive in charge of security.

1:39:59.860 --> 1:40:02.030
We all have our secrets,
Mr. Marlowe.

1:40:04.300 --> 1:40:06.790
